Soft Open Today & Friday: We are so excited to invite you in! While our official Opening Day is Saturday, we want everyone who has supported us to have a sneak peak today & Friday.

We are open 7:00am-3:00pm, every day, starting today, and available for walk-ins. Come by for Fancy Toast, French Toast, a Le Big Mac Omelette, Breakfast Tacos and our crispy Animal Style Hash Browns and more (our full menu is linked in our bio)!

We could not be more grateful for all the Pop Ups you attended, as that helped us shape our menu to where it is today. Carrie & Michael can’t wait to welcome you in (hugs are welcome!). We accept walk-ins only, so everyone can just come and enjoy us when they like!

We can’t wait to see you today and Friday (and on!). Thank you again for all the love and support! ❤️ 🥓

@foxandthehen_denver is Denver's newest and hottest breakfast and lunch spot located on 32nd in Lohi. It is brought to you by @michael_fox_denver (Fox) @chefcarrieb (Hen).

Michael is also currently the owner and Burrito Architect @dis.burrito, a Denver-based breakfast burrito wholesale business. Dis Burrito was born in his backyard during COVID lockdown summer 2020.

Baird competed on Season 15 of Bravo’s “Top Chef” where she quickly became a fan favorite and was a top 4 finalist. In the spring of 2019, Baird was a contestant on Food Network’s “Beat Bobby Flay” and beat him handily with her Pork Green Chili Huevos Rancheros. She was an All-Star judge on “Top Chef” Season 18, judging 8 episodes of the season.
